{"tid":215216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【今日跌啲乜】海航神秘靠山曝光！海航系全線捱沽","createTime":"2017-04-24T09:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T23:09:08.000Z","uid":73262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75177a500a0e49c48a1faa5ad09c37fa89c4414d","tid":215216,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T09:21:35.000Z","msg":"財雄勢大的海航集團近年高調走資，除了來港搶地，又在全球掃資產，早前遭踢爆其背後靠山疑涉王岐山家族，傳聞被中央調查兩者關係。海航神秘面紗被揭開，海航系見光死，股價全線下挫，其中海航實業（521）急瀉一成半，慘跌至兩年低位，全日報0.229元，成交6,519萬元。<br />\n<br />\n同是海航系的香港國際建投（687）挫3.7%，報3.4元；航基股份（357）走低4.7%，報6.67元；KTL（442）跌0.4%，報5.23元；鎮科集團（859）跌2.3%，報1.28元。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170424&amp;guid=56605721&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170424%26guid%3D56605721%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=973e2a96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170424%26guid%3D56605721%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=ede80a83\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170424&amp;guid=56605721&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"59401331afcc3bde8cb4e27ff7dbbad26f7c47ea","tid":215216,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T22:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4442b2319e72d31485bea2b40c1942cb19dd621","tid":215216,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T23:09:08.000Z","msg":"all in<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}